headline: Paychex Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., October 09, 2025--The Board of Directors of Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on Paychex common stock of $1.08 per share, payable on November 26, 2025, to shareholders of record as of November 7, 2025.
